# Step 2 — drill.  vhs demo/step2.tape
Output "assets/step-2-drill.gif"
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 22
Set TypingSpeed 28ms
Set Width 1180
Set Height 900

Hide
Type "source demo/rs-init.sh && clear"
Enter
Show
Sleep 500ms
Type "# drill into one repo - summary first, then the details"
Enter
Sleep 900ms
Type "rotscan checkout-api"
Sleep 350ms
Enter
Sleep 6000ms
